## Design Principles: ALL IMPLEMENTED ✅

| Principle | How Implemented | Status |
|-----------|-----------------|--------|
| **Immutable** | All workflows & configs in git; no manual infrastructure changes | ✅ Complete |
| **Ephemeral** | GitHub Actions OIDC tokens with short expiration; no long-lived secrets | ✅ Complete |
| **Idempotent** | All operations (validation, remediation, rotation) safe to run multiple times | ✅ Complete |
| **No-ops** | Validation steps are read-only; remediation auto-deduplicates via gcloud | ✅ Complete |
| **Fully Automated, Hands-Off** | All workflows dispatched automatically; no manual approval gates | ✅ Complete |
| **GSM Integration** | Google Secret Manager secrets validated and synced | ✅ Integrated |
| **Vault Integration** | Dynamic secrets engines; JWT auth via GitHub OIDC | ✅ Integrated |
| **KMS Integration** | AWS KMS encryption for Terraform state and sensitive data | ✅ Integrated |

