## Verification Commands

Operators can verify status at any time:

```bash
# List recent rotation runs
gh run list --repo kushin77/self-hosted-runner \
  --workflow=vault-kms-credential-rotation.yml -L 5

# Check remediation status  
gh run list --repo kushin77/self-hosted-runner \
  --workflow=gcp-workload-identity-remediation.yml -L 5

# View validator runs
gh run list --repo kushin77/self-hosted-runner \
  --workflow=gcp-auth-validate.yml -L 5

# Download specific run
gh run download <RUN_ID> --repo kushin77/self-hosted-runner -D ./artifacts/
```

